Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:17.88,text,,0,0,0,,{\pos(614,718)}我在 2012 年六月加入了馬圈。\N我不知道這將\N塑造我接下來的人生。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:22.48,text,,0,0,0,,{\pos(662,664)}這是我敬圈子的一首歌。\N敬友誼公主。
Comment: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1000)}公主，親愛的\NDear Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.81,0:00:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1000)}你是否在那？\NAre you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1000)}我一直在等\NI've been waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1000)}等你來這兒\Nwaiting for you here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1000)}一個新的世界，時機已到\NThe time has come for a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.24,0:00:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1000)}別在過去中迴轉\NDon't wander in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1000)}不曾知我已準備\NNever knew that I was ready
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1000)}它來的好快\NIt came on so fast
Comment: 0,0:00:58.36,0:00:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,## 間奏
Comment: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.98,0:01:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你造就一富城\NYou've made a kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}它會持續到時間盡頭\Nthat will last until the end of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我將回報你的教養\NTo tell you that you've raised me high
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在這封信裡頭\Nin my letter to you
Comment: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,## 間奏
Comment: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}從此岸到彼岸\NFrom sea to shining sea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們乘著回憶\Nwe carry memories
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}從世界各地\Nfrom everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每個物種都按時\NEverycreature knows their time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}公主，親愛的\NDear Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}時機已到\Nthe time has come
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你該走了\Nfor you to go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}戰局已勝\NThe battle's won
Comment: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,## 間奏
Comment: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,## 導歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}公主，求你幫我擦乾眼淚\NPrincess, please wipe these tears from my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不知我能否放手\NI don't know if I can let go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我所知道的一切\NEverything I've ever known
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}都是你所教\Ncame from you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}公主，我求你\NSo Princess, please
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不想離去\NI don't want to go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我學了好多\NI've learned so much
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我會傳承直到永恆\NI'll carry it all forever
Comment: 0,0:03:57.69,0:03:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:04:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}公主，親愛的\NDear Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們會盡全力\NWe'll try our best
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}帶著你所教一切\NTo take what you've taught us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一個偉大旅程\NA great new quest
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即使我們跌倒\NThough we may fall
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只要飛越天空\NFly through the air
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們永遠會記得\NWe'll always remember
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此間的魔法\NThe magic we shared
